[{"title":"初次搭建hexo心得","url":"http://yoursite.com/2018/07/21/初次搭建hexo心得/","content":"<h1 id=\"总述\"><a href=\"#总述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总述\"></a>总述</h1><p>搭建的过程分为以下几步<br> 1 安装node.js<br> 2 安装git<br> 3 安装hexo博客框架<br> 4 测试本地<br> 5 部署config以及github</p>\n<h1 id=\"安装node-js\"><a href=\"#安装node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装node.js\"></a>安装node.js</h1><p> Node.js下载地址：<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a> 安装过程默认</p>\n<h1 id=\"安装git\"><a href=\"#安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装git\"></a>安装git</h1><p>Git软件下载地址：<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://git-scm.com/download</a><br>安装过程默认</p>\n<h1 id=\"安装hexo\"><a href=\"#安装hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装hexo\"></a>安装hexo</h1><p>Hexo官方网站：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a><br>1 在本地找一个地方用来存放hexo<br>2 npm install -g hexo-cli<br>3 hexo init #初始化<br>4 hexo install #安装依赖包</p>\n<p>#测试本地运行<br> hexo g #等同于hexo generate 生成静态文件<br> hexo s #hexo server 启动本地服务</p>\n<p>#部署到github<br>1 在github创建一个项目，比如我的是tai769  则项目名称为 tai769.github.io，github.io不变，前面的最好用github的名字，至于为什么我也不知道，因为本身也是菜鸟学习。</p>\n<p>#部署到线上<br>1 打开_config.yml 找到ploy 修改成以下的 repo源填写你自己的项目地址<br>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/tai769/tai769.github.io.git\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/tai769/tai769.github.io.git</a><br>  branch: master<br>2 设置ssh连接<br>cd ~/.ssh<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “<a href=\"mailto:2217687104@qq.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2217687104@qq.com</a>“  # 这个地方添个人邮箱<br>将生成的pub文件里面的内容复制粘贴<br>3 登录github 设置 找到ssh和gpg keys<br>新建一个new ssh key 讲复制内容粘贴进去<br>4 输入 ssh -T <a href=\"mailto:git@github.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">git@github.com</a> 测试是否连接成功。如果看到hi后面是你的用户名，就说明成功了。</p>\n<h1 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h1><p>hexo clean<br>hexo generate<br>hexo deploy</p>\n<h1 id=\"心得\"><a href=\"#心得\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"心得\"></a>心得</h1><p>要注意ssh这个地方，要对应新的ssh-key 不然就会出现出错，导致你的本地可以访问，远程却不可以，至于为什么我也不知道，多看日志报错，还得记住坑人的新建文章命令什么的，下载markdown，开始写markdown，算是和之前的typecho比起来，比较繁忙的一点了吧。但是免费这一点也不错，各有各的好处把。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":["学习"]},{"title":"你好 态子","url":"http://yoursite.com/2018/07/20/你好-态子/","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"http://yoursite.com/2018/07/20/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"category","url":"http://yoursite.com/category/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"link","url":"http://yoursite.com/link/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"about","url":"http://yoursite.com/about/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"project","url":"http://yoursite.com/project/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"search","url":"http://yoursite.com/search/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"tag","url":"http://yoursite.com/tag/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]}]